Greetings from Shaastra 2017!

Onwards and upwards to our first event following the theme release,
Shaastra presents an assistive technology themed "Be The Eye" Marathon in
association with Western Digital Corporation.

The schedule of the event is as follows:-

Registrations - 3:30- 4:30 pm
Inauguration Address- 4:30 - 5:00 pm
Marathon - 5:00 - 6:00 pm
Basketball match for differently abled people - 6:15 - 6:30 pm
Prize distribution - 6:30 pm onwards

Starting Point : OAT

The Chief Guest:
The Inaugural Address will be delivered by our Chief Guest for the event,
P. Madhavi Latha, a multiple time National Paralympic Swimming medallist,
having won many awards and held important administrative positions in
paralympic sports.

T-Shirts and Certificates await all who shall run for the cause, and indeed
prizes worth 30000 INR for the winners of the event.

Regards
Animesh Bagora

